TEXT.TITLE: VANCOUVER STOCK EXCHANGE LISTS DIAEM RESOURCES
TEXT.BODY: The Vancouver Stock Exchange said it has listed the common stock of DiaEm Resources Ltd <DAE.V>, which has interests in an emerald property in North Carolina and a diamond property in Indonesia. Reuter
